Aspect	                    ON (Join Condition)                 	            WHERE (Filter Condition)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
When it is applied	        During matching of rows while joining	            After the join result is produced

Main purpose	            Defines how rows from two tables should match	    Defines which joined rows should remain in final output

Best for	                Keeping all rows from left/right table but          Filtering final output based on conditions
                            controlling what matches	
